Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Caused by Kamala Harris and Joe Biden, the humiliation in Afghanistan set off the collapse of American Credibility and Respect around the world. Our country will never be safe again until we have FIRED those responsible for this disaster. The VOTERS are going to fire Kamala and Joe on November 5th—and when I take office, I will ask for the resignations of every single senior official who touched the Afghanistan calamity to be on my desk at noon on Inauguration Day.
